    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.poster.avif?t=1746371581\" width=624 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.webm?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/b7b4999f49e8efc21f4ce243eae91a07.mp4?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>选择守卫者！</strong></h2></li></ul>从各种各样并拥有独特能力的角色中选择人物。交换你从战斗获得的战利品能让你解锁新技能和使用新武器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/d3486e9ff2b12c4a5f73b5d42732c565.avif?t=1746371581\" width=620 height=232 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>冲向战场！</strong></h2></li></ul>去发现不同的武器风格，角色特征和盖亚元素。在游戏过程中切换武器以改变战斗进程。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.poster.avif?t=1746371581\" width=624 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.webm?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/c95f0c2ba3286f8bc3c78242d31058c7.mp4?t=1746371581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索竞技场！</strong></h2></li></ul>探索如何利用环境来获得战术优势。每个竞技场都有多条路线、阻碍点和可解锁的捷径。进行团队合作与移动能力来控制整个竞技场。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1718290/extras/12b01e2bcc8ce2af5776c8fcd2d20437.avif?t=1746371581\" width=620 height=522 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为守卫者。成为盖亚。</strong></h2></li></ul>由独立开发者精心制作。自制游戏引擎包含在内。<br>针对 Steam Deck 进行了优化。",
